---
title: Spiced Beef Pilaf and Mango Chutney with Green Beans and Yoghurt
description: This Spiced Beef Pilaf and Mango Chutney is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R03_W14_UK_QF11743-22_Main_low-4c78e0d7.jpg
